---
import { Info } from "@lucide/astro";
---
<aside class="rounded-md bg-(--color-paper-2) border border-(--color-ink-200) p-5 flex gap-3" role="note">
  <Info class="w-5 h-5 text-(--color-brand-500) flex-none mt-0.5" />
  <div class="text-sm font-sans leading-relaxed text-(--color-ink-700)">
    <p class="font-semibold text-(--color-ink-900) mb-1">Disclaimer</p>
    <p>
      The information in this article is for general informational purposes only and does not constitute legal advice. Citations of statutes and case law are correct as of publication. For advice on a specific matter, consult a qualified advocate licensed to practice in the relevant jurisdiction.
    </p>
  </div>
</aside>
